      '| ATR-2026-00417 | CVE-2026-22252 | LibreChat MCP STDIO argument injection (argv-level shell metachars) |',
      '| ATR-2026-00418 | CVE-2026-22688 | WeKnora MCP plugin config-driven RCE (config-file as exec target) |',
