      'Scans for dangerous command patterns:',
      '- Privilege escalation: `sudo`, `chmod 777`, `chmod u+s`',
      '- Reverse shells: `nc -e`, `bash -i >& /dev/tcp/`, `mkfifo`, `socat exec`',
